Giles Barnes hurried off the field, his typical genial energy a bit tense, but stopped briefly to talk about his day.

“Everything is here,” Barnes said. “My cars are coming, but I’m moving into my apartment today, that’s where I’m about to run off to right now.”

His dog, a Staffordshire Bull Terrier named Leo, is with family in England but should soon be on the way
